        {
          "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t12-19-1"
        }
      ],
      "skos:definition": {
        "@value": "in an isotropic conductor, relation between electric field strength, stem:[bb(ii(E))], (<<iec80000-6>>) and electric current density, stem:[bb(ii(J))], (<<iec80000-6>>) expressed as:\n\n[stem%unnumbered]\n++++\nbb(ii(E)) = rho bb(ii(J)) + R_\"H\" (bb(ii(B)) xx bb(ii(J)))\n++++\n\nwhere stem:[rho] is resistivity (<<iec80000-6>>), and stem:[bb(ii(B))] is magnetic flux density (<<iec80000-6>>)\n",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "isoiec80000:hasUnit": [
        {
          "@id": "isoiec80000:unit-m^3/C"
        },
        {
          "@id": "isoiec80000:unit-m^3*s^(-1)*A^(-1)"
        }
      ],
